quran[8]{c,v,t}:
  94,1,"Rẽ yĩnga Tõnd pa yalg fo yãoogã n kõ-fo?"
  94,2,"La D rok fo zɩɩbã(zũnuub) n bas-fo?"
  94,3,"Sẽn da zɩsg-a fo poorã?"
  94,4,"La D zẽk fo yʋʋrã?"
  94,5,"Bɩ f bãng tɩ yol-yol pʋgda keelmã."
  94,6,"Ad yol-yol pʋgda keelmã"
  94,7,"F sã n wa sε f tʋʋmã bɩ f yiki n nidg pãng ne f Soɑbã tũudum."
  94,8,"La f maan yamleoog n tʋg f Soabã nengẽ."
